sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sp_css"><sp_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><css>div[data-angular-treeview] {
  /* prevent user selection */
  -moz-user-select: -moz-none;
  -khtml-user-select: none;
  -webkit-user-select: none;
  -ms-user-select: none;
  user-select: none;

  /* default */
  font-family: Tahoma;
  font-size:13px;
  color: #555;
  text-decoration: none;
}

div[data-tree-model] ul {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  list-style: none; 
  border: none;
  overflow: hidden;
}

div[data-tree-model] li {
  position: relative;
  padding: 0 0 0 20px;
  line-height: 20px;
}




div[data-tree-model] li .normal,
div[data-tree-model] li .collapsed,
div[data-tree-model] li .expanded{
  padding: 1px 10px;
}

div[data-tree-model] li i, div[data-tree-model] li span {
  cursor: pointer;
}

div[data-tree-model] li .selected {
  background-color: #aaddff;
  font-weight: bold;
  padding: 1px 5px;
}</css><name>Angular Treeview CSS</name><sys_class_name>sp_css</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>danny.haile@itgfirm.com</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-10-30 00:40:26</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>6a3267c0db6deb00b86770c08c961931</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Angular Treeview CSS</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Purchase Request" source="x_naci_purchase_re">bbd9a2eedbc1ab4054d8ff621f9619c6</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Purchase Request">bbd9a2eedbc1ab4054d8ff621f9619c6</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sp_css_6a3267c0db6deb00b86770c08c961931</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>danny.haile@itgfirm.com</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-10-30 00:40:26</sys_updated_on></sp_css></record_update>
